title: Las Vegas Bombshell: Video Appears to Show Muzzle-Flash From 4th Floor, Not 32nd (Video)

Las Vegas Bombshell: Video Appears to Show Muzzle-Flash From 4th Floor, Not 32nd (Video)
Monday, October 2, 2017 14:00
% of readers think this story is Fact. Add your two cents.
The following is from the Red Elephants and I’ve found several videos below claiming the same thing. As well as videos of police scanner feeds during the horrible tragedy that took place. You can check out the videos below and here is the original twitter feed and feed back from the source.
I have no idea if this video is real or click-bait but it appears to show muzzle-flash coming from somewhere around the 4th floor, not the 32nd. In my video from earlier today I showed you a video in which I couldn’t seen any muzzle-flash coming from the upper floors of the building. Well, this might explain some of that. Notice how small the flash is compared to the windows. It looks about right in terms of size at least. I can’t verify the source but I thought you guys might want too see it.
You can clearly see shots being fired from the 4th floor. Was there another shooter? #VegasShooting #PrayForVegas pic.twitter.com/UlVElrptXY
Witness footage of gun attack on Las Vegas music festival – excess of 100 were injured when a ‘lone wolf’ gunman fire multiple shots at the Route 91 harvest country. There was a shooter on 32nd floor of the Mandalay Bay. She is an Asian female, approximately 4ft 11in, weight of 111lbs. There are of course saying there was a female asian companion from many sources. Stay tuned for more info from BIN on this tragic situation. Prayers to the families.
